      • getLocation

        public java.util.List<Location> getLocation(java.lang.String protocol,
                                            java.lang.String path,
                                            java.lang.String metainfo,
                                            Project project,
                                            GlobalSearchScope scope)
        Description copied from interface: SMTestLocator
        Creates the Location list from protocol, path, and metainfo in scope. Implementation of test framework can provide additional information in metainfo parameter, The metainfo parameter simplifies the search for locations, but can not be used to identify the test. A good example for code>metainfo is the line number of the beginning of the test. It can speed up the search procedure, but it changes when editing.
        Specified by:
        getLocation in interface SMTestLocator
